description: Our focus is Traditional/Global BBQ and Gourmet Sandwiches featuring fresh, all natural and local ingredients. As firm believers that there is no better way to connect to people than sharing great food, our values are core to everything we do...•Charity — We give back to the community that supports us, and we LIVE that by example. •Community — We support other local businesses and farmers, and LEAD by example.•Culture — Nostalgic, but creative... quirky, but fearless... We are Southern, and we LOVE by example.
name: CockADoodleMoo Truck
